<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #F8F7F4; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 32px auto; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #E5E3DC; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #F59E0B; padding: 28px 32px; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .body { padding: 28px 32px; }
    .post-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1918; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 12px; }
    .post-summary { font-size: 14px; color: #6B6963; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #0A6E8A; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn-secondary { background: #F59E0B; margin-left: 8px; }
    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E5E3DC; margin: 24px 0; }
    .notice { background: #FEF3C7; border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px 18px; font-size: 13px; color: #92400E; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .stats { background: #F8F7F4; border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px 18px; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: #6B6963; }
    .stats strong { color: #1A1918; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 32px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6B6963; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>SlimFile 블로그 검토 요청</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <div class="notice">
        AI가 새 글 초안을 생성했습니다. 검토 후 발행해 주세요 — 승인 전에는 발행되지 않습니다.
      </div>

      <p class="post-title"><%= @post.title_ko %></p>

      <% if @post.meta_description_ko.present? %>
        <p class="post-summary"><%= @post.meta_description_ko %></p>
      <% end %>

      <a href="https://slimfile.net/blog/<%= @post.slug %>" class="btn">미리보기 →</a>
      <a href="https://slimfile.net/admin/posts/<%= @post.id %>/edit" class="btn btn-secondary">편집·발행 →</a>

      <hr class="divider">

      <div class="stats">
        발행 제안일: <strong><%= @post.published_at&.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M") || "-" %></strong><br>
        카테고리: <strong><%= @post.category %></strong> ·
        남은 블로그 주제: <strong><%= @remaining_topics %>개</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      SlimFile &mdash; slimfile.net
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
